125
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:01,120
Kali ini, anda kurang bernasib baik.

126
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:03,600
Raffy merakam video awak dan Arnold.

127
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:16,080
Walaupun anda berkata tiada apa yang berlaku,
