145
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:33,360
Jika ya, pergi cari seseorang.

146
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:36,240
Bukan saya tak cari.
Saya tidak menemui yang betul.

147
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,960
Fokus dan selesaikan lukisan.

148
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:40,480
Bagaimana keadaan di sini?

149
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,200
Ini, ambil sedikit air.

150
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,080
Terima kasih.

151
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:51,880
Patutkah kita merancang perjalanan
atau melakukan sesuatu bersama-sama?

152
00:10:53,833 --> 00:10:54,833
Apa yang berlaku kepada anda?

153
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:57,760
Malam pembukaan dalam dua minggu.

154
00:10:58,520 --> 00:10:59,760
Saya tak nak awak stress.

155
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,160
Awak tak nak pergi ke?

156
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:03,760
